nodes.text: Rinnas Edu was a Human male who lived on Tatooine during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. While his farmstead was attacked by the Sand People, he tasked a Republic spacer to assist him in repairing the vaporators in the Northern Jundland Wastes. Thanking the spacer's help, Rinnas continued to defend his farmstead.
